OL,3,CSNP demands two-child cap be scrapped
OL,4,C'immediately'
OL,6,FThe SNP has tabled an amendment
OL,7,Fcalling for the two-child cap to be
OL,8,Faxed, with the party's Westminster
OL,9,Fleader Stephen Flynn branding a new
OL,10,Fchild poverty taskforce set up by the
OL,11,FLabour government as a "cynical
OL,12,Fattempt to kick the issue into the
OL,13,Flong grass".
OL,15,FWhile some within Labour want the
OL,16,Fcontroversial policy to be abolished,
OL,17,FSir Keir Starmer ruled out making such
OL,18,Fa change in his first King's Speech as
OL,19,FPrime Minister.
