OL,6,FInstead the Government announced a new
OL,7,Ftaskforce shortly afterwards, which
OL,8,Fwill look at "all the available levers
OL,9,Fwe have across government" to deliver
OL,10,Fthe "ambitious" child poverty strategy
OL,11,Fpromised in Labour's manifesto.
OL,13,FThe SNP has tabled an amendment to the
OL,14,FKing's Speech calling for the two-
OL,15,Fchild cap to be scrapped "immediately"
OL,16,Fas a "vital first step in tackling
OL,17,Fchild poverty".
