OL,6,FIf selected, the amendment will go to
OL,7,Fa vote next week, with Mr Flynn
OL,8,Finsisting: "It's shameful that Keir
OL,9,FStarmer has made the political choice
OL,10,Fto continue imposing Tory austerity
OL,11,Fcuts, instead of delivering the change
OL,12,Fthat people in Scotland were promised."
OL,14,FThe policy was introduced by the
OL,15,FConservatives in 2017 and prevents
OL,16,Ffamilies claiming Universal Credit or
OL,17,Fchild tax credits for a third child,
OL,18,Fexcept in very limited circumstances.
