OL,6,FMr Flynn said: "The Labour government
OL,7,Fshouldn't need a taskforce to find a
OL,8,Fconscience and do the right thing.
OL,10,F"This cynical attempt to kick the
OL,11,Fissue into the long grass won't wash
OL,12,Fwith voters.
OL,14,F"For every day that Starmer dithers
OL,15,Fand delays, more children will suffer
OL,16,Fthe consequences of Labour inaction.
OL,18,F"The cap must go ` and it must go now."
